# What is Apache Spark?

> **Apache Spark™** is a unified analytics engine for large-scale data processing.

Spark is a distributed cluster-computing framework that allows to perform data processing on a large scale across clusters. It supports Java, Scala, Rlang, and Python.

paragraphs.title: Create a Jar full of M&Ms
paragraphs.text:
import scala.util.Random

val colors: Seq[String] = Seq("Blue", "Green", "Yellow", "Red", "Brown")

val random = scala.util.Random

// Let's create our M&M's Jar
val mmsJar = Seq.tabulate(random.nextInt(250000 - 120000))(n => colors(random.nextInt(colors.size))).toDF("color")


mmsJar.show()

import org.apache.spark.SparkFiles

spark.sparkContext.addFile("https://github.com/pcm-dpc/COVID-19/raw/master/dati-andamento-nazionale/dpc-covid19-ita-andamento-nazionale.csv")

val covidData = spark.read.format("csv")
    .option("inferSchema", "true")
    .option("header", true)
    .load(SparkFiles.get("dpc-covid19-ita-andamento-nazionale.csv"))

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions

val tamponiCasi = covidData
    .withColumn("rapporto_tamponi_casi", functions.round($"totale_casi".divide($"tamponi") * 100, 2))
    .select("data", "tamponi", "totale_casi", "rapporto_tamponi_casi")

tamponiCasi.show()
tamponiCasi.createOrReplaceTempView("tamponi_casi")

paragraphs.text:
val window = org.apache.spark.sql.expressions.Window.orderBy("data")

val tamponiCasiGiornaliero = covidData
    .withColumn("tamponi_diff", $"tamponi" - lag("tamponi", 1, 0).over(window))
    .withColumn("totale_casi_diff", $"totale_casi" - lag("totale_casi", 1, 0).over(window))
    .withColumn("rapporto_tamponi_casi", functions.round($"totale_casi_diff".divide($"tamponi_diff") * 100, 2))
    .select("data", "tamponi_diff", "totale_casi_diff", "rapporto_tamponi_casi")
    
tamponiCasiGiornaliero.show()
tamponiCasiGiornaliero.createOrReplaceTempView("tamponi_casi_giornaliero")

SELECT tc.data, tc.rapporto_tamponi_casi AS tc_rapporto, tcg.rapporto_tamponi_casi AS tcg_rapporto
FROM tamponi_casi AS tc
INNER JOIN tamponi_casi_giornaliero AS tcg ON tcg.data = tc.data
